              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-emerald-600 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
                <span class="text-slate-700">Check for rust spots breaking through the painted finish</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-emerald-600 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
                <span class="text-slate-700">Check the anti-skid pattern on high-traffic planks for wear that's smoothed it down</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
