                <span class="text-slate-700">Check if the hooks and locks are properly fixed, as rainwater may have loosened the hooks and locks or shifted the frame connections.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 pt-5 border-t border-slate-300 font-bold mt-2">
                <span class="text-emerald-600 font-bold mt-0.5">&rarr;</span>
